features: 【Multiple Pockets】This weekender bag has a total capacity of 45L and is designed with multiple pockets to keep your daily necessities organized. The main compartment has enough space to store travel clothing, T-shirt, pants, toiletries, and other travel essentials,or gym equipment. There is a zippered pocket in the front and 2 zip side pockets for easy access. The duffel bag perfect and reliable companion for weekend overnight trip, fitness.

【Wet-Storage Pocket】 The wet pocket in the main compartment with waterproof PVC material can help you to separate dry items from wet items. Great for wet swimsuits or damp towels. In addition, this travel duffel bag also gives an extra small toiletry bag for easy storage.

【Independent Shoe Compartment】Weekender travel bag comes with a large independent shoe compartment, storing 1-2 pairs of shoes( less than size of 11) or dirty clothes, two venting hole in shoe compartment, make it keep breathable to not smelly. It can help you avoid dirtying other clothes when packing, also provide more convenience for your travel.

【Carry on Bags For Airplanes】 Medium Travel Bag: 21.3 x 9 x 13.8 inches. Weight: 1.45lb; The medium duffel bag meets most international carry-on requirements. Fits in the overhead compartment as well as the under seat as Personal Items in flight.The weekender duffle bag equipped with back sleeves that will keep it in place on main roller suitcase, to free your hands when you're at the airport.

【Durable Material and Multi Carrying Ways】Made of Water Resistant and Durable Polyester Fabric with double zippers. Ensure a secure & long-lasting usage everyday & weekend. Adjustable shoulder straps and comfortable Handle provides many convenient way for your weekend and overnight travel, it can be used as handbag, shoulder bag, duffel bags for traveling, personal item travel bag, sport gym bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great weekend bag at an affordable price
reviews.reviewText: Great weekend bag with a nice amount of space. I particularly loved the vented area for a pair of shows. I didn't want to spend a lot of money, but wanted something that would hold up and be sturdy. I believe I found the bag I was looking for. I believe time will tell, but it seems very well built.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Huge Bag, Good Construction
reviews.reviewText: This review is for the medium-sized weekender bag. I wanted this bag for a long weekend getaway and it actually let me pack more than I needed. At the size it is, I could pack more than a week’s worth of clothes and stuff in it.The fabric and construction of the bag are fine. The various pockets and straps are helpful for organizing and carrying.I do wish it had some stabilizer in the shoe compartment to help it hold its shape. That and a zipper around the bottom to compress the shoe compartment when it’s empty would be improvements I would have liked.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Holds a fair amount of stuff
reviews.reviewText: This bag can hold a decent amount of items! I am using for my vacation travels where I can bring small appliances and it is great for carting these items around! Everything is in one bag and I always have it packed and ready to go! I only wish it was just a tiny bit bigger, but it's still a much easier way to pack.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Travel Bag
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice looking strong bag with many pockets and options that make it well suited for travel, gym, etc.There are 3 small zippered pockets on the outside. The bottom unzips and provides a ~3" high vented section meant for shoes, but you could obviously put anything you'd like in there.The main compartment can store a lot of clothing and is opened with a nice double-zipper (which the bottom shoe pocket also offers). All zippers are smooth. There are several non-zippered pockets in the main compartment (fine if the bag stays upright) and a larger waterproof zippered pocket that is meant for wet items (bathing suit, etc).It has padded canvas handles. It also comes with a small basic toiletry bag and an option to attach a decent shoulder strap.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Roomy And Made To Last
reviews.reviewText: This bag is made well and holds a lot of stuff to be considered a size medium. I like that this has metal clips for the strap because those tend to last a little longer. I also like that the strap has fairly decent padding on it. This bag seems pretty durable to me and the asking price seems fair. I think it's a nice weekender bag and would recommend it to others.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lightweight bag but sturdy
reviews.reviewText: This travel bag is lightweight but sturdy. It is made of canvas. My favorite aspect of this bag is all the pockets. You have 2 on the end. 3 small pockets on the inside for toiletries or socks. Then a larger pocket for swim suits or dirty clothes and finally a shoe compartment on the bottom. The strap has a small shoulder cushion. Decent at best. The toiletries bag is small and basic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very nice bag. Came in a nicely packed box, neatly folded. The material and construction are outstanding. Well made. Looks expensive. Lots of compartments. It's big enough but not obnoxious. Love the color. Got this for a gift and I'm super exited about it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty good size, fairly sturdy
reviews.reviewText: I got this for a duffel gym bag for my husband and it may be just on the large size for that, but it's very nice to have the bottom shoe/wet item container underneath the bag. The bag is fairly sturdy, maybe not as thick as it could be overall but I think it will be pretty durable. It has handles and a shoulder strap which is nice for versatility. And it comes with a bonus little matching toiletries bag, very convenient.
